LINES OF DECEIT : COCAINE AND THE WHITE HOUSE / produced by Eric Schwartz and Corey Dubin. - Documentary from interviews about the ways in which drug smuggling has been, and is currently being used to finance secret wars and illegal operations by agencies of the United States government. 

Features interviews with: Pedro Alcontrar, Columbian Senator| John Stockwell, for CIA agent| Daniel Sheehan, chief cousel for the Christic Institute| and Louis Wolf and Bill Schapp, editors of "Covert Action." - 

RECORDED: 31 Aug. 1990

See more at: http://pacificaradioarchives (dot) org/recording/sz0576#sthash.SKFO2331.dpuf
